WEBVTT

00:01.560 --> 00:02.880
<i>( Horn honking )</i>

00:02.880 --> 00:04.520
<i> I'm Alex Mack.</i>

00:04.520 --> 00:06.200
<i> I was just an average kid</i>

00:06.200 --> 00:07.880
<i> until an accident
changed my life.</i>

00:07.880 --> 00:09.960
<i> And since then...</i>

00:09.960 --> 00:12.680
<i> Nothing's been the same.</i>

00:12.680 --> 00:14.080
<i>( Zapping )</i>

00:16.000 --> 00:22.074
Advertise your product or brand here
